    "section_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/request-forms/#about-form-fields",
    "section_text": "The way HTML forms ( <form></form> ) sends the data to the server normally uses a \"special\" encoding for that data, it's different from JSON.\n\nFastAPI will make sure to read that data from the right place instead of JSON.",
